    "description": "Are you looking for a job? Aye, we need a new bar staff in the Thieves’ cave. The tipsy thieves are very demanding customers! There is no time for mistakes! If you make the boys wait too long they’ll be raging. If you mess up you're done here! So are ya ready for your first day?<br><br><strong>Game mechanics</strong><br><br>You are a bartender trying to make money for your favourite band's gig. To your surprise, the band members are regular customers at the bar. Fulfil their orders as quickly as possible. The longer you take the more angry they get so make sure to check the anger meter!<br><br>Pick up drinks and snacks at the bar and bring the ordered refreshments to the band members. The boys might ask you to play a certain song using the jukebox.<br><br>If you want a break from your job, you can have fun using the karaoke machine.<br><br>Apart from orders, each day one of the members has a quest for you. Be a good person and help them! <br><br>Will you make it to your dream gig?",
